seo: wavlink, wl-wn535k2_firmware, os命令注入, 漏洞检测
seo_en: wavlink, wl-wn535k2_firmware, os command injection, vulnerability detection
summary: 该插件用于检测WAVLINK WN535K2和WN535K3设备中的OS命令注入漏洞，通过向/cgi-bin/nightled.cgi发送特定POST请求，验证是否存在漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect OS command injection vulnerabilities in WAVLINK WN535K2 and WN535K3 devices by sending a specific POST request to /cgi-bin/nightled.cgi to verify the existence of the vulnerability.
